&lt;b&gt;Temps d&#39;incantation&lt;/b&gt; 1 &lt;a class=&quot;pagelink&quot; href=&quot;Types-Dactions.html#SIMPLE&quot; title=&quot;Action simple&quot;&gt;action simple&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;b&gt;Composantes&lt;/b&gt; &lt;a class=&quot;pagelink&quot; href=&quot;Pr&#233;sentation-Des-Sorts.html#COMPOSANTES&quot; title=&quot;composantes&quot;&gt;V, G, M&lt;/a&gt; (un morceau de tissu brod&#233; de moins de 3&#160;m de c&#244;t&#233; d&#39;une valeur de 100 po)&lt;br/&gt;
